Detailed Description

Dimension types, to use as template parameters for Quantity. All dimensions that are not a base, irreducible dimension are defined as products of powers of other dimensions.

Typedef Documentation

typedef mpl::vector_c<int,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0> dimensionless

Dimensionless scalar:.

Available if you have a unit-less, dimension-less coefficient: don't use it to avoid declaring the dimensions of values! That would defeat the purpose of using this module.
